{"bangumi":{"date":"2010-10-27","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/26/86/9639_fY4eM.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/26/86/9639_fY4eM.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/26/86/9639_fY4eM.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/26/86/9639_fY4eM.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/26/86/9639_fY4eM.jpg"},"summary":"　　由苍树梅老师创作的四格漫画「向阳素描」，在新房及SHAFT的制作小组合作下，围绕向阳四子由乃、小宫、寻及沙英展开的动画在今年年初已经顺利播放了第三季，并一如以往四子的萌力在动画中大放异彩，成为值得推介的作品。向阳的故事是讲述向往着美术班的由乃，在离开父母后住进一间名为“向阳庄”的宿舍，并遇上形形色色的人。向阳庄以怪人群聚而闻名，因此每天都过着手忙脚乱的生活。而在第三季中，向阳四子升了一个年级，也出现新的学妹乃莉及小荠，向阳庄的六个房间第一次住满了人，变得非常热闹。而照着前两季动画的传统，第三季动画终于决定了特别篇的制作。","name":"ひだまりスケッチ×☆☆☆ 特別編","name_cn":"向阳素描×☆☆☆ 特别篇","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":243,"total_cont":0},{"name":"新房昭之","count":237,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SHAFT","count":170,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":160,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百合","count":135,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2010","count":130,"total_cont":0},{"name":"芳文社","count":111,"total_cont":0},{"name":"向阳素描","count":109,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":98,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":71,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"阿澄佳奈","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"睡前动画","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻百合","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"梅老师是最萌的CV","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"苍树梅","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2010年10月","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"向阳素描×☆☆☆","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"蒼樹うめ","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"四格","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2010年","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"石仓贤一","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"后藤邑子","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"長谷川菜穂子","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"新谷良子","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"沙发套","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"